vgp - Video Get Podcast

USAGE:
    vgp

DESCRIPTION:
    Fetch podcasts from configured podcast feeds, apply date filters,
    and queue matching podcasts for download. Processes all configured
    podcast feeds and filters content based on publication date (and other user-based criteria).

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-videos-podcast-feeds FEEDS
        Space-separated list of RSS podcast feed URLs

    -conf-videos-podcast-days-back DAYS
        How many days back to fetch (default: 7)
        NOTE: this is meant to run nightly, so really, 1 would be ideal to minimize IO

EXAMPLES:
    vgp

NOTES:
    The script uses the current date as a cutoff point and only processes
    podcast episodes published after the configured days-back period.
    Requires proper RSS feed configuration to function correctly.
